      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code verification through documented benchmark tests sufficient for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Solver verified against analytical solutions for Poiseuille flow and lid-driven cavity benchmarks. Order-of-accuracy testing confirmed second-order spatial convergence for the discretization schemes employed. Results archived in project verification log VL-2023-07."
