      "rationale": "Test sample characterization beyond what is required for validation boundary condition specification is not required at MRL 2. Fluid analog properties (density, viscosity) measured and reported in experimental protocol EP-FDA-2022."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
