      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; differences between validation and COU inputs noted qualitatively.",
      "rationale": "Formal equivalency assessment not required at MRL 2. Qualitative review of differences between validation test inputs and COU device inputs performed and documented in technical note TN-2023-09. Key differences (impeller geometry, operating speed range) assessed as within acceptable extrapolation range for the intended decision."
